          "plain_text": "There’s one classic drunk guy outside who takes a liking to me. He repeats my name consistently for about five minutes at a time and then promptly forgets it. He slurs a lot, so I didn’t get all the words from his stories, but if my suspicions are correct he had a wild time with his boss in Cape Town many years ago. ",
