    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "To make the whole situation more absurd; the content of Alan’s talk was on embracing the chaos and disorder that is life - I can safely say that I understood what he was saying in that moment. ",
