          "text": {
            "content": "The rest of the drive was less eventful. Plus I’m tired now and don’t really care much for describing the beautiful roads, ever growing mountains and their gravitational pull, remarkably good quality roads for KZN and my arrival at Khotso in the dark to be welcomed by the cutest and fluffiest cat that seems that have taken a fancy for me. Goodnight!",
